鏈啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢大撚把 睇見都火</blockquote><br />\n買d貴野比佢曬命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e725243b578928271b268383c575e2e0d18d858","tid":120341,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T11:50:06.000Z","msg":"送個仆街仔畀佢囉"},{"pid":"a8c7a771f494404596685eb49d981d4c4b05f746","tid":120341,"uid":25952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T12:00:00.000Z","msg":"求其去pandora 買粒珠比佢咪算"},{"pid":"1f202a94c95e6e7c2e0a38f6ee1977b6ec46f9ca","tid":120341,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T12:10:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩日打孖黎先好呀<br />\n如果分開又要兩份禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n經驗話我知，就咁紀念日冇咁易記得。情人節就冚世界都係送花收花，仲有個師奶班所謂閨蜜啊，一到二月一四叫撚曬春咁㗎，都痴撚線，冇得避冇得避。"},{"pid":"dfca0b35349969abf31b814bf0f500bab3693c54","tid":120341,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T12:13:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>求其買條頸鏈啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢大撚把 睇見都火</blockquote><br />\n買d貴野比佢曬命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最後都諗住買啲護膚品算㗎啦，我都唔識睇。"},{"pid":"ae0d42e62b325bc9c5f5f0d764d73c6f6926e278","tid":120341,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T12:15:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>送個仆街仔畀佢囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講起個衰仔，唔射佢埋牆真係益左佢了，由細到大夾埋佢老母撚鳩我"},{"pid":"9ba00e393181d69418fad8df1c8ae9ee27d47332","tid":120341,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T12:15:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>求其去pandora 買粒珠比佢咪算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽講玻璃嚟喎"},{"pid":"c70b511aa7115083c07ef9e8ff56a8cebedeb6ed","tid":120341,"uid":23376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T12:21:56.000Z","msg":"個仔幾歲？"},{"pid":"58c705bd3a2c10791d55a015bbed98bfc2ef2f58","tid":120341,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T14:44:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個仔幾歲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n19啦"},{"pid":"aee13e19d62846118fa219162846b1a99db329fc","tid":120341,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T14:47:07.000Z","msg":"同阿仔驗埋dna穩陣<br />\n咁擺你上枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc526aaa8af8629649e85e95c23b5a76e2615c4","tid":120341,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:00:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>送個仆街仔畀佢囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講起個衰仔，唔射佢埋牆真係益左佢了，由細到大夾埋佢老母撚鳩我</blockquote><br />\n樓主講野好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2b8883e40313ea77f59ccaf47990091e39b2a4","tid":120341,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:01:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同阿仔驗埋dna穩陣<br />\n咁擺你上枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n帽事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7cd46bb26e8dd4e08f317ca536eb7e0beeea41","tid":120341,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:02:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>送個仆街仔畀佢囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講起個衰仔，唔射佢埋牆真係益左佢了，由細到大夾埋佢老母撚鳩我</blockquote><br />\n樓主講野好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da254ff5fecb765d2810e4f88d3a76bf5e9728a","tid":120341,"uid":2997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:03:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個仔幾歲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n19啦</blockquote><br />\n笑撚死 最後買左咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c912141893ba39f6d673a7879fb56c29353984","tid":120341,"uid":714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:03:28.000Z","msg":